Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:04.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:07.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:16.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you didn't know how to deal with things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that no one showed you how to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you become my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:30.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Madness can't be suppressed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You were quite wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:58.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't like your taste in music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:05.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Off he goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:10.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, this key can open it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:14.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that girl's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:23.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the wavelength of the Great Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The black blood has stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:15.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like we have a winner for the second battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Both souls' responses have eased up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And Maka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Maka alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:23.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:27.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have matched the Devil Sword's wavelength well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.14,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Sword's wavelength is stabilizing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I cried this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to deal with the tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka, there's no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We should move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't leave her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess around, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! So little!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you, what did you do?! Why is my master like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Become friends with Chrona?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it funny to become friends with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, it's still boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! It has to be bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:22.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it succeed? It's a great way to relieve stress, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You one star Technician!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Chrona's real friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:36.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrona, how dare you hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I feel, being hit by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a poo which couldn't come out for three days,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...which when you suddenly push out with all you got,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...makes the water in the toilet basin splash you. That kind of feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't understand such a vulgar example!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me. Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we entrust him to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:27.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shrine Of The Seal:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Prepared By The Immortal Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone caught up with the ones carrying the black blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A black crust stopped the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:53.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it healed by itself when the black blood disappeared from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:58.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did the black blood inside you disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if a Kishin gets the black blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to catch up with Kid-kun and Black Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-kun went this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:29.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm missing out on my big entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's dark so I can't stand out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Your loud voice already stands out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We have to get to Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty wrecked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...like entrails made of ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:54.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop staring around. It's fine as long as you don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus your mind on symmetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The number eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Do you need aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel a Kishin's wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:41.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt this much pressure before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kishin is inside there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Another silly question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:57.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this from father, so I don't know much about the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat Asura, {\alphaHFF}he removed his skin... and sealed him with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat Asura, he removed his skin... {\alphaHFF}and sealed him with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat Asura, he removed his skin... and sealed him with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father in the past was pretty scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:12.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To create a sack to seal Asura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To carry Asura's soul, {\alphaHFF}body... and madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To carry Asura's soul, body... {\alphaHFF}and madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To carry Asura's soul, body... and madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,His own face was the most suitable to seal him with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Father took all of Asura's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...turned him into a powerless body and put him into the sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Asura's body... {\alphaHFF}yearns for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Asura's body... yearns for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're giving him the black blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-kun, heat response ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A ranged attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil's Eye Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:05.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so occupied with the Kishin's madness that I didn't notice him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:09.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An immortal body, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trying to do this fair and square is useless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:20.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have to break his balance and take him out in that opening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When it comes to mobility I'm better than him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I breach him even once, he won't be able to keep up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two attacks at my feet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, he's targeting my speed this way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:36.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:37.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Resonance, {\alphaHFF}Execution Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Resonance, Execution Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Resonance ratio stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Noise 1.8%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Feed back in 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:09.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This should at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? Death Cannon didn't slow him down?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this range, this is bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz, Patty. It's coming! Don't go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kid-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This soul response...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tagut-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tagut-tan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:00.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:01.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tagut-tan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sazakuya's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sazakuya's?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this range, this is bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must regain distance immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He won't come at me recklessly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he gets close for an attack,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...he'll always try to protect his legs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something to connect together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:12:00.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That pillar and this pillar were once a single pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And it fell down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That way they connect nicely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:15.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that! It's not that I was thinking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was actually bothering me though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Kid! Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's doing puzzles, I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a fool of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:34.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, where's the arm that fell from that statue?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:39.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What absurdity! That elephant, the trunk is missing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up! It's irrelevant!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use...{\alphaHFF} no... stop....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use... no... {\alphaHFF}stop....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use... no... stop....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That pillar, could it fit that way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, {\alphaHFF}elephant, trunk, left, below, above, right, nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, elephant, {\alphaHFF}trunk, left, below, above, right, nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, elephant, trunk, {\alphaHFF}left, below, above, right, nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, elephant, trunk, left, {\alphaHFF}below, above, right, nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:51.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, elephant, trunk, left, below, {\alphaHFF}above, right, nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, elephant, trunk, left, below, above, {\alphaHFF}right, nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:52.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, elephant, trunk, left, below, above, right, {\alphaHFF}nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:52.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pillar, elephant, trunk, left, below, above, right, nose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:58.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, even though he's inside a place like this, he was doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he'll lose his mind and end up being driven by madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:07.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. He started scratching his head, he's started thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:16.14,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? We have to fix the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our... no, it's my victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity but there'll be no Kishin resurrection!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, the one who has the black blood is further ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what? That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This way we can get Kid's attention on the Werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:49.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:54.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is only wearing that ball on his left foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:04.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, you! I don't forgive anyone who stands in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:05.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:06.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:07.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The problem is this other kid...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:19.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,From above?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong with this Kid? Is he joking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's weird, this physical unease...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He didn't try to avoid my attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:46.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is he frantically avoiding Black Star if he's immortal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see, I get it now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? I'll tear you into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the number eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it, go ahead and try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The "you" that stands before me can't do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems this is as far as it gets...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Eye... this is your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Warding Vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:34.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic that projects a live feed of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a mess on my tadpole's head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't do this we wouldn't move ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't try to evade my shots...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:53.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't want to be hit by Black Star's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:58.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd really be hit, we'd find out that it's not a real body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:02.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The first attack was shot from behind the image right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That was to make us believe the image was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:10.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, since I was afraid of your immortal body, I stuck to long ranged attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good trick to be used by an immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you notice when you cut him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, 'cause you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:24.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When I cut him with the knife, I was thinking "what a great technique!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides Tsubaki would notice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:33.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking "Black Star has grown up," and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Technician is an idiot, the Weapon is one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We've wasted a lot of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get rowdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Such nice, obedient students, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Stein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:03.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,They completed every task you gave them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You can feel it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:10.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It wants to blow out... the Kishin's madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing it, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you struggle, it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How to raise a good child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadpole...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, tadpole?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look, Eruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:06.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kishin is inside there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry or those kids will catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My face... Please Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:09.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,An immortal like me is going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A hallucination?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:29.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Kishin's madness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... {\alphaHFF}inside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... inside there.
